OL,3,CDad-of-two told he could die within
OL,4,Cfive years after 'muscle twitch'
OL,6,FA father-of-two and rugby coach has
OL,7,Fspoken of how an innocuous muscle
OL,8,Ftwitch led to the devastating
OL,9,Fdiagnosis that he could lose his life
OL,10,Fwithin five years.
OL,12,FCraig Eskrett, 36, from Hull, found
OL,13,Fout in September last year that he had
OL,14,Fthe debilitating condition motor
OL,15,Fneurone disease (MND).
OL,17,FIt came a year after he first started
OL,18,Fto experience symptoms.
