OL,3,CDad-of-two told he could die within
OL,4,Cfive years after 'muscle twitch'
OL,6,F"I noticed my thighs were twitching
OL,7,Fand at the time I thought it was just
OL,8,Fmuscle fatigue because I do a lot of
OL,9,Fsport and exercise," he said.
OL,11,F"So I thought I'd change my training
OL,12,Fregime.
OL,14,F"But when it came to the back end of
OL,15,Fthat year I started to have cramps
OL,16,Fduring the night, I couldn't put my
OL,17,Ffinger on why. At this point I was
OL,18,Fstill able to function well.
