OL,3,CDad-of-two told he could die within
OL,4,Cfive years after 'muscle twitch'
OL,6,F"(Then) I started to lose a lot of
OL,7,Fbalance when I was running. I played
OL,8,Fone of the games and felt like I
OL,9,Fcouldn't kick any more. There was no
OL,10,Fstrength."
OL,12,FVisits to a GP and physiotherapist
OL,13,Ffollowed, but after a referral to a
OL,14,Fneurologist Mr Eskrett was sent a
OL,15,Fletter confirming his diagnosis. He
OL,16,Fwas told he could have two to five
OL,17,Fyears
