OL,3,CDad-of-two told he could die within
OL,4,Cfive years after 'muscle twitch'
OL,6,F"It was hard because my partner was
OL,7,Fopposite me," he said. "She broke
OL,8,Fdown, which to me was probably the
OL,9,Fhardest part.
OL,11,F"I don't think it sank in until I
OL,12,Fstarted ringing my family and ringing
OL,13,Fmy friends."
OL,15,FMND affects the nerves in the brain
OL,16,Fand spinal cord which send messages to
OL,17,Fmuscles to allow movement.
