OL,3,CDad-of-two told he could die within
OL,4,Cfive years after 'muscle twitch'
OL,6,FHe said he was inspired by the
OL,7,Fextraordinary fundraising efforts by
OL,8,Fformer Leeds Rhinos stars Rob Burrow
OL,9,Fand Kevin Sinfield following Burrow's
OL,10,FMND diagnosis in December 2019.
OL,12,FHe told ITV News: "There are so many
OL,13,Freasons why it needs more backing
OL,14,Fbehind it really. Until it gets into a
OL,15,Fplace where people do get the
OL,16,Fdiagnosis. That we're in a place that
OL,17,Fwe can support it much better."
