OL,6,FMr Eskrett says he is determined to
OL,7,Fdefy his prognosis, saying it is "at
OL,8,Fthe back of my mind (but) the thing
OL,9,Fthat keeps driving me and keeps me
OL,10,Ffighting this every day".
OL,12,F"Since I've been diagnosed I've put
OL,13,Fweight on I feel like I'm getting
OL,14,Fstronger. A switch has gone on and
OL,15,FI've got that motivation to beat it
OL,16,Fand it's amazing the amount of support
OL,17,FI've received from friends and
OL,18,Ffamily," he said.
